            <thetext>All textfield should offer the feature of a placerholder text if nothing is entered. Its quite common in other frameworks to visualize the text, that should be entered, as grey and italic text as long as nothing has been entered. Also hints could given for e.g. the proper format to enter the text. Widgets that could benefit from such a change are.
- textfield
- passwordfield
- datefield
- combobox</thetext>
